Prerequisite: Install Node

Please install the following packages:

npm init
npm install modules
npm install -g nodemon
npm install ejs express body-parser sqlite3

Run the application:
nodemon index.js

Open the following link
Note: Please note that the port for the node in my system is 3001. It might be different for others. For convienence,
        I have console.logged the port number where the node js runs so that it will be easy to identify the port number
http://localhost:3001/
